00:10:54.028 --> 00:10:55.029
Karube!

00:10:57.114 --> 00:10:58.157
Sorry.

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:00.618
- I needed to get something.
- What do you mean, "sorry"?

00:11:05.623 --> 00:11:07.083
Shibuki and I…

00:11:07.750 --> 00:11:09.377
For us, there's no tomorrow.

00:11:12.088 --> 00:11:13.381
Why, what's going on?

00:11:14.757 --> 00:11:15.841
Don't be angry.

00:11:21.430 --> 00:11:23.182
We're wasting time. Let's go.

00:11:25.226 --> 00:11:26.268
Come on.

00:11:28.062 --> 00:11:29.063
Thank you.

00:12:30.916 --> 00:12:33.544
Let's do this.

