on your acceptance, Hajime.

00:26:52.485 --> 00:26:54.821
You really accomplished something.

00:26:54.904 --> 00:26:56.990
I know your mother would be happy too.

00:26:57.073 --> 00:26:59.618
And this is just the beginning.

00:27:01.244 --> 00:27:03.747
I'll see it through.
I don't want to end up like Ryohei.

00:27:04.372 --> 00:27:08.126
I can't teach Ryohei anything,
but you're different.

00:27:08.209 --> 00:27:09.919
Inside you, there's ambition.

00:27:10.920 --> 00:27:13.173
You're very different from your brother.

00:27:15.842 --> 00:27:18.595
Ryohei, why don't you come over
and join us?

00:27:30.815 --> 00:27:34.069
If you're happy being a loser…

00:27:35.403 --> 00:27:38.281
…then let me be the wolf!

00:27:42.994 --> 00:27:44.663
Arisu!

00:27:53.421 --> 00:27:56.341
Five minutes remaining.

00:27:58.551 --> 00:28:00.053
I've had enough.

00:28:01.930 --> 00:28:06.476
I don't care who survives in the end.

00:28:11.523 --> 00:28:12.524
But…

00:28:14.401 --> 00:28:17.696
But I don't want it to end this way.

00:28:40.051 --> 00:28:42.721
Is this about Arisu and Chota again?

00:28:48.685 --> 00:28:52.063
You know, you really are very kind.

00:29:37.734 --> 00:29:39.319
I don't expect anything from you

00:29:39.402 --> 00:29:41.571
and you never fail to disappoint me
in that regard.

00:29:43.239 --> 00:29:44.365
So, did you…

00:30:32.789 --> 00:30:34.374
This noodle is so good!

00:30:39.462 --> 00:30:41.172
You look like you can't eat noodles…

00:30:45.301 --> 00:30:46.386
Come on, man!

00:30:47.262 --> 00:30:49.138
Come on, Karube, faster!

00:31:10.994 --> 00:31:12.161
Guys.

00:31:14.873 --> 00:31:17.750
I got this… dream.

00:31:18.585 --> 00:31:22.255
I wanna buy a huge farm in Australia.

00:31:23.423 --> 00:31:28.511
Then I'll invite you guys over,
and we'll drink beer in the morning.

00:31:28.595 --> 00:31:30.221
That sounds nice!

00:31:30.305 --> 00:31:32.765
And I'll deliver
triple grade-A steaks to you

00:31:32.849 --> 00:31:35.518
with my drone delivery service.

00:31:35.602 --> 00:31:38.563
My drones will be fully automated,
I'll develop an app for them!

00:31:40.398 --> 00:31:43.610
All right then.
Cheers to our future.

00:31:43.693 --> 00:31:44.861
Cheers!

00:31:44.944 --> 00:31:46.946
You better keep your promise,
you hear?

00:32:38.748 --> 00:32:40.917
Three minutes remaining.

00:32:53.429 --> 00:32:56.140
Guys, I'll… quit.

